                    <comment id="13193868" author="olegk" created="Thu, 26 Jan 2012 14:45:06 +0000"  >Long time, no speak.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
There is no good reason. What we can do is to deprecate LayeredSchemeSocketFactory interface and create a new one (say, LayeringSchemeSocketFactory or some such) and provide a compatibility layer for LayeredSchemeSocketFactory similar to that for LayeredSocketFactory.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Oleg</comment>
